<h1 class="header-tos"><center><b>Privacy Policy</b></center></h1>

<section class="mg-top-20">
  Pollios values your privacy and your personal information, as well as your content in our service. This Privacy Policy explains what information Pollios Co., LTD (“Pollios”, “we” or “us”) collect about you, why, and what we may do with that information.
</section>

<div class="header-title">Information Collection and Use</div>
<section class="mg-top-20">
<ol>
  <li>Your Personal Information <p>We collect your email address to create your account and to communicate with you. We also collect your name and your photo to show in your Profile screen. Optionally, you can give us more information about yourself, such as birthday, gender, hometown, in the Profile setting screen, to allows us to filter and customize our contents for you and learn your preferences better.</p></li>
  <li>The Content Your Created in Pollios <p>Pollios allows you to create your own polls and participate in voting other polls. Your poll may include many photos. We collect all the poll and vote data in our service to provide application service. We may display some of your “public polls” and their vote results in public places. We will never display your nonpublic polls and vote results. We respect your vote to remain anonymous if you chose to do so and will never display your name in any place in such case.</p></li>
  <li>Activity Log <p>We anonymously log application usages. Screen access, time on screen, etc. This is not associate with your user account by any mean. We use this information solely for study application usage for future improvements of usability and functionality.</p></li>
</ol>
</section>


<div class="header-title">Cross-Border Data Transfers</div>
<section class="mg-top-20">
We do not share your personal information with any 3rd party. We, however, may share your public polls and their vote results, as well as your profile screen as displayed in our application, with any 3rd party as well as in public. We also share statistic and demographic of voters.
We may share all the data with our partner parties and parent companies.
</section>

<div class="header-title">Data Security</div>
<section class="mg-top-20">
We store all your data in secure servers, encrypt your personal information, and take very cautious approach to prevent loss, misuse or alteration of your personal information.
</section>


<div class="header-title">Policy Update</div>
<section class="mg-top-20">
We may update this policy at any time. We will send you a notification in our mobile application when we do so.
</section>


